I know some for me, some slots are a pain to upgrade gear wise. Being that i have to cater for my melee and spell casting side it can get fun deciding.<br>
<br>
My question is what did people pick for there classes 'odd' slot, the odd slot can be anything you like - but usually the one or two slots you can never get a perfect match in.<br>
<br>
For me right now my odd slots are:<br>
<br>
Ear: <br>
Face:<br>
Wrist:<br>
Waist:<br>
Gauntlets:<br>
Range:<br>
Finger:<br>
<br>
Earings and Fingers are a pain - but with the PoP jewlery for Valor &amp; Tactics you can get two very nice items, also the Cazic Thule drops are nice to. (Valorium ring of Gallantry, Bloodmetal earing of engagement, Ring of slime, Mosquite leg earing)<br>
<br>
Gauntlets - grr hard for shadowknights, paladins, rangers. There are a lot of nice warrior gauntlets but knight ones are super-crappy. Would be quite interested to find out what people chose and why, off top my head Velious royals are probably one of the better gauntlet types.<br>
    And do people hold out for runes for this exact reason?<br>
<br>
Bracers - lot of crappy bracers i have seen, Spirit wracked cords are the nice quest ones and then you have the bracer of speed from another nice dragon excursion. Failing that i didnt see much that beats Benevolence bracers.<br>
     What are people picking and why? i have the bracer that i want and will not change it for a while, just curiouse as to what others are useing and why.<br>
<br>
Face - Again, lot of crappy helms and masks, mask is hard for me as i cant track down a good one and i hate stormfeather. Sitting on crystal spider eyes.. just because of the hastle to get a nicer mask. <br>
     Mask seems to be a great hastle, this one is curiousity post as there are not many nice masks out there so we all go for the same ones *grins*.<br>
<br>
Waist - i am guessing people try to get haste out of the back/waste slot, there are some nice belts out there now from the worms. This is a combination question really - Assuming you could choose the slot you have haste in wich belt would you go for and why, possibly cloak to.<br>
     Why this interest me the most is there are some nice hybrid FT cloak from ME and why i am not aiming for one i can imagine a few people choosieng FT over a few extra HP or resists, and then picking a belt to match, i know some people use an AoB belt also.. so many combination options.<br>
<br>
So this is more a what you use and why, i am not looking for upgrade advice, more of an idea of how people maximised what they have instead of pick everything.<br>
<br>
